title: QLS Classic: Prince Paul
itunes:title: QLS Classic: Prince Paul
description:
Legendary producer and DJ Prince Paul talks about his contributions to early Hip-Hop, winning Grammys with Chris Rock and some of the ways he shaped the sound of De La Soul, 3rd Bass, Queen Latifah, and more.
